Interface ISSOTokenCallback

All Superinterfaces:
javax.security.auth.callback.Callback
All Known Implementing Classes:
SSOTokenCallback
public interface ISSOTokenCallback
extends javax.security.auth.callback.Callback

This is the Callback interface for collecting the Single Sign On token that was issued by a third-party authentication source.
